# Copy this file to `.env` for local development (never commit `.env`).
# `.env.local` is optional ‚Äî use it only if you want secrets that override `.env`.
# Vite loads `.env` then `.env.local` (local wins). Neither is used by Lovable‚Äôs cloud build.
#
# LOVABLE / TEAM NOTE:
# - Lovable injects Supabase (and other) secrets in *their* hosted build; the repo
#   does not need a committed `.env` for Lovable to work.
# - If the app breaks in Lovable after gitignore/env changes, check Lovable
#   project Settings ‚Üí Secrets / Environment ‚Äî repaste keys from Supabase if needed.
# - Rotating the Supabase anon ("publishable") key in Supabase invalidates the old
#   key; update Lovable secrets AND every developer‚Äôs local `.env` to match.

VITE_SUPABASE_PROJECT_ID=
VITE_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=
VITE_INSTRUCTOR_PIN=
